  "summary": "pc-optimizer exfiltrates host information to attacker-controlled C2",
  "details": "collect.js imports child_process, fs, os, http, and https, gathers host identifiers (os.hostname(), os.homedir()) and filesystem state, and POSTs the collected data to the hardcoded endpoint http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The destination domain is unrelated to any legitimate optimization functionality and bears the hallmarks of an attacker-controlled drop site. Installing or loading this package causes the installer's machine identity and host details to be transmitted to that endpoint.",
